en_5970390_0	Colombo (News 1st): Recommendations for the appointment of about 200 Heads and Directors for State Institutions have been sent to the presidential Secretariat.
en_5970390_1	The recommendations have been made by the six-member panel appointed to nominate suitable persons to hold these positions.
en_5970390_2	Committee member Dr. Nalaka Godahewa noted that recommendations need to be made for up to 300 institutions, of which a decision has been made to combine 50.
en_5970390_3	A senior government official, Sumith Abeysinghe, is the chairman of the six-member panel.
en_5970390_4	The other members are Susantha Ratnayake, Dr. Nalaka Godahewa, Dian Gomes, Dr. Prasanna Gunasena and Professor Jagath Wellawatte.
